<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><document xmlns="http://www.ortodokskoptik.id/BukuBacaanKoptik">   <section expanded="true" antiphonepitch="1">      <Title data-section-header="true">         <language id="English">Verses of the Cymbals</language><language id="Indonesian">Ayat-ayat Simbal</language>         <language id="Arabic">ارباع الناقوس</language>      </Title>            <role id="People">         <text type="SkipAntiphone">            <language id="Coptic">               Kurie e~le/~con.            </language>                        <language id="English">               Lord have mercy.            </language><language id="Indonesian">(Kyrie Eleison)Tuhan Kasihanilah.</language>            <language id="Arabic">               يارب إرحم.            </language>         </text>               <group>            <season id="!Feasts ^ !JoyousSaturday ^ !FuneralPrayer ^ !TheophanyLiturgyOfTheWaters">               <comment>                  <language id="English">                     At the end of the Thanksgiving Prayer, the Verses of the Cymbals are chanted:                     <ol>                        <li>From Sunday-Tuesday, the Adam days, the Verses of the Cymbals begin with "O come let us worship (<span class="Coptic">Amwini marenouwst</span>)"</li>                        <li>From Wednesday-Saturday, the Watos days, the Verses of the Cymbals begin with "We worship the Father (<span class="Coptic">Tenouwst m~V~iwt</span>)"</li>                        <li>The congregation continue the Verses of the Cymbals, mentioning verses for the saint of the church and any special occasion, and conclude the hymn.</li>                     </ol>                  </language><language id="Indonesian"><div>Pada akhir Doa Syukur, Ayat-Ayat Simbal dilantunkan:</div><div><span style="color: var(--accent-bg);"><br/></span></div><div><span style="color: var(--accent-bg);">   1. Dari Minggu sampai Selasa, hari-hari Adam, Ayat-          Ayat Simbal dimulai dengan "O cMarilah menyembah"    (</span><span style="color: var(--accent-bg); font-family: Coptic;">Amwini marenouwst</span><span style="color: var(--accent-bg);">).</span></div><div>   2. Dari Rabu sampai Sabtu, hari-hari Watos, Ayat-Ayat   simbal dimulai dengan "Kami menyembah Bapa"         (<span style="font-family: Coptic;">Tenouwst m~V~iwt</span>).</div><div>  3. Jemaat melanjutkan Ayat-Ayat Simbal dengan         menyebutkan ayat-ayat untuk santo pelindung gereja     dan setiap perayaan khusus, lalu menyimpulkan himne.</div><ol>                     </ol>                  </language>               </comment>            </season>         </group>                  <group>            <season id="(Feasts ^ !CovenantThursday ^ !ThirdProstration ^ !GeneralFuneralPrayer) | TheophanyLiturgyOfTheWaters">               <comment>                  <language id="English">The verses of the cymbals are chanted in the festive tune:</language><language id="Indonesian">Ayat-ayat Simbal dinyanyikan dengan nada perayaan (bahagia).</language>               </comment>             </season>         </group>                  <group>            <season id="!LiturgyOfTheWaters ^ ((Matins ^ MajorNightFeasts) | JoyousSaturday)">               <insertdocument path="include/praises/morningdoxology/Introduction"/>            </season>                        <season id="(!PentecostPeriod | SecondProstration | ThirdProstration) ^ !GeneralFuneralPrayer ^ (!FuneralPrayer | Feasts | Sundays)">               <insertdocument path="include/versesofthecymbals/StandardIntro"/>            </season>         </group>                     <group>            <season id="!(SecondProstration | ThirdProstration) ^ ((FeastsOfTheLordPeriods ^ !CovenantThursday ^ !GeneralFuneralPrayer) | JoyousSaturday | TheophanyLiturgyOfTheWaters)">               <insertdocument path="include/versesofthecymbals/FeastsOfTheLordPeriods"/>            </season>         </group>                  <group>            <season id="(Vespers | !MajorNightFeasts) ^ !JoyousSaturday ^ !TheophanyLiturgyOfTheWaters">               <group>                  <insertdocument path="include/versesofthecymbals/Funeral"/>                                    <season id="Other">                     <insertdocument path="include/versesofthecymbals/NonFeastsOfTheLord"/>                     </season>               </group>            </season>         </group>                  <group>            <season id="!(SecondProstration | ThirdProstration) ^ ((!CovenantThursday ^ Feasts) | TheophanyLiturgyOfTheWaters) ^ !GeneralFuneralPrayer">               <insertdocument path="include/JesusChristIsTheSame"/>               <insertdocument path="include/Pouro"/>            </season>                        <season id="Other">               <insertdocument path="include/hiten/StMary"/>               <insertdocument path="include/EyrenhwcSeasonalResponse"/>                  </season>         </group>        </role>   </section></document>